</div><h1>Tuolumne Grove</h1><div>
<br>We still had about a half of the day left with Amber, so after hiking down we headed to the Tuolumne and Merced groves.&nbsp; A lot of folks seemed tickled that we'd gotten married in Yosemite -- we got a ton of "congratulations!" and a few folks asked to take pictures for their own personal trip documentation.&nbsp; My favorite comment followed another couple telling us "Good luck on your marriage!" -- this long-haired guy said under his breath "you don't need luck" before getting into a camper that had "362 days since Florida!" written on the back.<br><br>Tuolumne Grove was about forty minutes from Tunnel View, which as a nice driving break.&nbsp; Also Yosemite is gigantic.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi8yMmI5M2Q3Zi1mY2M4LTQxMGUtYjI0YS0zYjk0YTlhMzcyYWM_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--db067d276a4297dbac78c4f46f8c115a23ead696" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWt5TW1JNU0yUTNaaTFtWTJNNExUUXhNR1V0WWpJMFlTMHpZamswWVRsaE16Y3lZV01HT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--cab0c2c24fd525c38b3efd839275eefd43c8b959/IMG_0179.jpg" filename="IMG_0179.jpg" filesize="678404" width="640" height="853" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="I love these huge trees"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
    <img src="{% imageUrl 'src/images/IMG_0179.jpg' %}">

  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      I love these huge trees
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br>We hiked down to the grove -- about a mile or so and another five or six hundred feet of elevation change -- and then toured some of the famous trees.&nbsp; This is called a tunnel tree, perhaps you can guess why:<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9mYWQyOTU1ZC00ZDU5LTQwYTAtOWRlMy1mMWY3N2RkNTZiYmE_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--7925c2815c77d9e598bf69d24d98f85b9e264551" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxtWVdReU9UVTFaQzAwWkRVNUxUUXdZVEF0T1dSbE15MW1NV1kzTjJSa05UWmlZbUVHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--ee2db0b4b3daf7c494ed96ab478b78781f0a58ff/IMG_0182.jpg" filename="IMG_0182.jpg" filesize="596141" width="640" height="853" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="it's because it's within sight of a tunnel that cuts through a mountain"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
