</div><h1>The End</h1><div>
<br>We returned from the Merced Grove hike around 2:30 or 3:00 and our time with Amber was up.&nbsp; She -- and all of the Adventure Instead folks that we interacted with -- was awesome.<br><br>Afterward we returned to our cabin in Wawona.&nbsp; We grilled some chicken and summer squash, and roasted potatoes for dinner.&nbsp; The cabin had a fire table, which is like a table that is 40% less convenient to use (although it does look cool).<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi80NzI0YWEzOS04Y2E5LTRhMDUtOGNjMC00NTI1ZmNkNjA1Y2M_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--d61a8c6fa52c0ffa125fe273e96448fe23356afa" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWswTnpJMFlXRXpPUzA0WTJFNUxUUmhNRFV0T0dOak1DMDBOVEkxWm1Oa05qQTFZMk1HT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--84bba8460eb876f4d66d50a3270740ae2cfea46b/IMG_2888.jpg" filename="IMG_2888.jpg" filesize="199279" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="so much flame right by your forehead!"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
