  <figcaption class="attachment__caption">
      I really like portrait mode
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>Taft Point itself opens to a large rock-and-scrub plateau after emerging from the trees.&nbsp; Deep fissures scar the sides of the plateau.&nbsp; They're so big.<br><br>
</div><div>
<action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi82YWEwYmYxYS1lZTc2LTQ4NWItYTIyMS0wOWFkMTJlNTNmY2I_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--3af59cf0f1a6876e40c55dc6999082cda2db4201" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWsyWVdFd1ltWXhZUzFsWlRjMkxUUTROV0l0WVRJeU1TMHdPV0ZrTVRKbE5UTm1ZMklHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--affa56910e3644cc77ec465d8dd0628e125c02b2/IMG_2912.jpg" filename="IMG_2912.jpg" filesize="377683" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="you could fit like a hundred Carries into that fissure"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
