      just straight down if you look over this cliff
  </figcaption>
</figure></action-text-attachment><br><br>Other folks don't seem to have this problem.&nbsp; There were a group of folks hanging out on a ledge, cheering each other on as they slack-lined across part of the point.<br><br><action-text-attachment sgid="BAh7CEkiCGdpZAY6BkVUSSJXZ2lkOi8vYW4tZXZlbnQvQWN0aXZlU3RvcmFnZTo6QmxvYi9iYWQ4MDFkZi02NjliLTRjMjktYTY3ZS0wNTIxNDI5MzQwNDg_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIgxwdXJwb3NlBjsAVEkiD2F0dGFjaGFibGUGOwBUSSIPZXhwaXJlc19hdAY7AFQw--1e5f4673f8a4af76b267d0bc337646263e8e8997" content-type="image/jpeg" url="https://www.carrie-truman.fyi/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaEpJaWxpWVdRNE1ERmtaaTAyTmpsaUxUUmpNamt0WVRZM1pTMHdOVEl4TkRJNU16UXdORGdHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6ImJsb2JfaWQifX0=--6d00a47af0fd90ce925d5b0ff2a455da7dd451e1/IMG_2917.jpg" filename="IMG_2917.jpg" filesize="240669" width="640" height="480" previewable="true" presentation="gallery" caption="center-left is a crazy person"><figure class="attachment attachment--preview attachment--jpg">
